# Vibes - Minimal PWA Project Structure

## Project Overview
Vibes is a minimal, bi-color PWA built with Next.js 14, TypeScript, and modern CSS. The project focuses on simplicity, accessibility, and clean design using only black and white colors that adapt to system theme.

## Project Philosophy
- **Minimal**: Keep everything as simple as possible
- **Bi-color**: Only use black (#000000) and white (#ffffff)
- **Responsive**: Mobile-first, clean design
- **Modern**: Use latest CSS features and clean typography
- **PWA**: Proper progressive web app implementation

## Directory Structure
```
vibes/
├── app/
│   ├── layout.tsx          # Root layout with PWA metadata
│   ├── page.tsx            # Minimal home page
│   └── globals.css         # Bi-color theme with system support
├── public/
│   ├── manifest.json       # Simplified PWA manifest
│   └── icons/              # SVG icons for PWA
├── .cursor/rules/          # Cursor AI rules
└── package.json            # Minimal dependencies
```

