## Design Guidelines
- **Colors**: Only white (#ffffff) and black (#000000)
- **Typography**: Inter font family with clean hierarchy
- **Spacing**: CSS custom properties for consistency
- **Animations**: Subtle transitions (respecting prefers-reduced-motion)
- **Theme**: Automatic light/dark mode based on system preference

## Development Standards
- **Framework**: Next.js 14 with App Router
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Modern CSS with custom properties
- **Components**: Minimal, functional components
- **PWA**: Proper manifest, meta tags, and offline support

## CSS Approach
- CSS custom properties for theming
- System color scheme support (light/dark)
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Safe area support for mobile devices
- Minimal animations with performance optimization

## PWA Requirements
- Proper manifest.json configuration
- Essential meta tags for PWA installation
- System theme color support
- Touch-optimized interactions
- Standalone display mode support

## Development Commands
- `npm run dev` - Start development server
- `npm run build` - Build for production
- `npm run start` - Start production server
- `npm run lint` - Run ESLint
- `npm run test-local` - Build and serve locally
